Sales Revenue Analysis Dashboard

 Project Description

This project aims to analyze sales and revenue data using an interactive dashboard. The dashboard provides insights into sales performance, revenue trends, and top-performing products.

Objectives

* Analyze sales data efficiently.
* Monitor key performance indicators (KPIs).
* Identify revenue trends over time.
* Compare product and regional performance.
* Support data-driven decision making.

 Features

* Data import from Excel/CSV.
* KPI visualization.
* Revenue trend analysis.
* Product-wise sales analysis.
* Region-wise revenue analysis.
* Interactive filters and slicers.

Tools Used

* Power BI / Excel
* CSV Dataset
* Data Visualization

 Key Metrics

* Total Sales
* Total Revenue
* Total Orders
* Average Revenue per Order

 Conclusion

The dashboard helps users understand sales patterns and business performance through visual reports and analytics.
